room_title: Escape room "Cursed" by Escape Rehoboth in Rehoboth Beach
room_address: 20245 Bay Vista Rd. Rehoboth Beach, DE 19971
room_description: You and a group of other “adventure tourists” are on the final leg of a round-the-world trip to various ancient and mysterious sites. Along the way (much like any typical traveler might do) everyone has collected souvenirs and artifacts from their journey. You’ve returned home and are preparing to meet one of your fellow travelers to recount your journey when you receive word he is missing. Something’s gone terribly wrong…
